  "prompt": "How is IIM Vishakapatnam doing with regard to exposure and placements. Is it better than IMI Delhi?",
  "response": "When comparing IIM Visakhapatnam and IMI Delhi, it's important to consider various factors such as industry exposure, placement statistics, faculty, curriculum, and other opportunities. As of the latest available data, here's a comparison:\n\n### IIM Visakhapatnam:\n1. **Industry Exposure**: \n   - Being part of the prestigious IIM brand, IIM Visakhapatnam benefits from its growing network and connections with various industries.\n   - The institute invites a range of industry leaders for guest lectures, seminars, and workshops.\n\n2. **Placements**:\n   - IIM Visakhapatnam has been showing a positive trend in placement statistics over the years, with good average packages and diverse roles offered across sectors.\n   - The placement process is supported by a dedicated placement cell that actively engages with recruiters and alumni to broaden opportunities.\n\n3. **Growth and Opportunities**:\n   - As a relatively new IIM, it has been expanding its infrastructure and academic offerings.\n   - It also benefits from mentorship and collaboration with IIM Bangalore, adding significant value to its academic framework.\n\n### IMI Delhi:\n1. **Industry Exposure**:\n   - IMI Delhi, being one of the older management institutes in India, has established strong industry connections.\n   - The institute regularly organizes conclaves, industry visits, and interactive sessions with corporate leaders.\n\n2. **Placements**:\n   - IMI Delhi consistently has robust placement records, with numerous prominent companies visiting the campus.\n   - It has a wide alumni network, which helps in maintaining strong relationships with a variety of recruiters across industries.\n\n3. **Reputation and Alumni Network**:\n   - IMI Delhi has a rich legacy and a solid reputation, contributing to its strong placement records and industry presence.\n   - Its alumni network is extensive, which helps current students in networking and career opportunities.\n\n### Conclusion:\nBoth IIM Visakhapatnam and IMI Delhi have their unique strengths. IIM Visakhapatnam is part of the IIM brand, which comes with its own set of advantages, especially as it continues to grow and make its mark. Meanwhile, IMI Delhi has the benefit of a longer legacy, established industry connections, and a robust alumni network. \n\nChoosing between the two would depend on your priorities\u2014whether you prefer the brand value and growing opportunities of IIM Visakhapatnam or the established reputation and network of IMI Delhi. It is also advisable to look at the most recent placement reports and specific program offerings to make a well-informed decision.",
